     C           #DATA9    ENDSR
**  MSG
 INCORRECT ORDER NUMBER.
 THERE IS NOT DATA.(PARTS) (EXEC.= F12)
 ECECUTE PARTS&DIE ORDER DATA SAMMARY PROC.(CANCEL ONLY)
 ECECUTE PARTS ORDER DATA SAMMARY PROCESS (EXEC.= F12)
 ECECUTE DIE ORDER DATA SAMMARY PROCESS (EXEC.= F12)
 THERE IS NOT DATA.(DIE) (EXEC.= F12)
 THERE IS NOT DATA.(PARTS & DIE)(CANCEL ONLY)
 SELECT A PRINTER.
